    "course_title": "PRACTICUM IN FINITE ELEMENTS",
    "description": "Use of finite elements (FE) for solving practical problems in mechanics. Elementary theory of FE is discussed. A commercial computer program is used for applications. Major emphasis is on behavior of FE, modeling, and evaluation of results for correctness.",
